CustomField.description: This field is optional. It is manually populated by a user. When the value of the field is set to true, the sharing setting of this Relationship is affected to restrict read/write access. This field is used to indicate that the relationship is subject to Regulation O standards. If Checked, the relationship is regulation O.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: This field should be checked if Regulation O applies to this Relationship
CustomField.label: Reg O Relationship
